Links : 
https://www.linuxbuzz.com/install-minikube-on-ubuntu/

Some Basic Commands : 

sudo apt-get install 
sudo apt-get install curl - To send data using syntax 

Some Commands : 
kubectl run my-first-pod --image=nginx --port=80  --restart=Never 
kubectl get pods 
kubectl exec -it my-first-pod -- /bin/bash - (To open shell in Container) 
kubectl get nodes .
kubectl get pod -o wide 
kubectl get pod -o yaml 
kubectl get pod -o json 

